---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-scartech">
		<p>&copy; {currentYear} Scartech Solution. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
		<p>Automatizando o que era manual e levando sua empresa para o futuro.</p>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.2rem;
		margin-top: auto;
		padding: 2rem 1rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		color: #1976d2;
		font-size: 1rem;
		background: #f8fbff;
	}
	.footer-scartech {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-scartech p {
		margin: 0.2em 0;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	footer a:focus {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.group {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.socials {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		footer {
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: space-between;
			padding: 2.5rem 5rem;
		}

		.group {
			flex-direction: row;
			gap: 1rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.socials {
			justify-content: flex-end;
		}
	}
</style>
